4. That the Capitall and moſt Antichriſtian oppreſſion of Tythes be taken away, and that Gleabe-Lands be ſold to ſatisfie Impropriators:
Provided their Tenure be not: from Biſhops, Deanes and Chapters, or Colledges, or their Eſtates under Sequeſtration;
And Goſpell-Miniſters to be maintained by a free Contribution, according to Goſpell-Order.
